    "created_at": "2016-08-26T08:51:51Z",
    "updated_at": "2016-08-26T08:51:51Z",
    "body": "I might pass this one on to @zcbenz or @kevinsawicki as they can probably give a super duper standpoint on this.\n\nMy current understanding is that we use Chromium's menus in our implementation of Menu's on Windows and Linux and use the native implementation on macOS.\n\nI tried to see how Atom handles this and I discovered that they steer clear of Dynamic Menus (as far as I can see).\n\n> As for the reported issue: I have no control over the ellipsis in the menu so I cannot even do the ellipsis myself because I have no information about the valid length until the \"...\" \n\nAh, I see what you mean.  Can't customly ellipsis it if you don't know the length to ellipsis too ðŸ˜¢ \n"
